                <td>Fresh Sliced Tomatoes</td>
                <td>1-2
            </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        
        <p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Let the Pizza Dough Rise for half an hour
</p>
        <p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Pre-heat oven to 425-450F
</p>
        <p><strong>Step 3:</strong> After dough has risen, roll out with a pin and/or stretch by hand
</p>
        <p><strong>Step 4:</strong> Add Mozzarella, Tomatoes, Basil, and Salt
</p>
        <p><strong>Step 5:</strong> Bake for 15-20 minutes
</p>
        
